# SauceDemo Playwright — Trace Viewer Integration

A Playwright suite with full **Trace Viewer** integration — every test
method generates a `.zip` trace file containing a step-by-step playback
of every action, DOM snapshot, screenshot, network request, and console
log. Failed tests open the Trace Viewer automatically.

---

## 📋 Project Overview

Playwright's Trace Viewer is the most powerful debugging tool in the
framework. This project wraps every `@Test` method with
`context.tracing().start()` and `context.tracing().stop()` so no test
run is ever lost. Traces are saved per browser per test method. On
failure, the viewer opens automatically in the browser. An Extent HTML
report is also generated with embedded failure screenshots.

---

## 🔍 What the Trace Viewer Shows

Opening any `.zip` trace file gives a full interactive timeline:

- **Before/after DOM snapshot** for every action
- **Screenshot** at each step — click to see exactly what was visible
- **Network requests** triggered by each action
- **Console logs** emitted during the action
- **Java source reference** — which line of code triggered each step

---

## 🏗️ Architecture
src/test/java/
├── base/
│   └── BaseTest.java                  # @BeforeMethod start trace
│                                      # @AfterMethod stop + save trace
├── data/
│   └── UserData.java
├── listeners/
│   └── PlaywrightListener.java        # Logs results to Extent report
├── pages/                             # All page classes unchanged
├── utils/
│   ├── TraceUtil.java                 # Saves trace, opens viewer on failure
│   ├── ScreenshotUtil.java            # Full-page PNG on failure
│   └── ExtentReportManager.java       # Singleton Extent instance
├── workflows/                         # All workflow classes unchanged
└── tests/
├── AuthWorkflowTest.java
├── ShoppingWorkflowTest.java
└── CheckoutWorkflowTest.java

## 📁 Output After Every Run
traces/
├── chromium/
│   ├── testValidLogin.zip
│   ├── testAddSingleItemToCart.zip
│   └── testFinishOrder.zip
├── firefox/  └── ...
└── webkit/   └── ...
screenshots/
├── chromium/
│   └── testFinishOrder_2024-01-15_14-32-07.png  ← failure only
└── ...
reports/
└── ExtentReport.html


